---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section class="box skills">
  <div class="skill">
    <header class="skill-head">
      <Icon icon="code" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2rem" gradient />
      <h2>Full-stack by default</h2>
    </header>
    <p>
      Happy moving between a React SDK, a backend service, a Terraform module,
      or a data pipeline in the same week. To me, it's all about the big picture, not a single piece of the puzzle.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="skill">
    <header class="skill-head">
      <Icon
        icon="strategy"
        color="var(--accent-regular)"
        size="2rem"
        gradient
      />
      <h2>Drawn to root causes</h2>
    </header>
    <p>
      The bugs I enjoy most are the ones that have stumped other engineers,
      races, feedback loops, silent data issues. I'd rather spend a week on
      the real cause than ship a workaround.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="skill">
    <header class="skill-head">
      <Icon
        icon="rocket-launch"
        color="var(--accent-regular)"
        size="2rem"
        gradient
      />
      <h2>Pragmatic about performance</h2>
    </header>
    <p>
      Latency, cost, and cluster headroom are numbers I actually watch. Most
      of my wins come from measuring before optimising and knowing when
      "fast enough" is the right answer.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .skill {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .skill-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
      column-gap: 5rem;
      row-gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .skill {
      display: grid;
      grid-row: span 2;
      grid-template-rows: subgrid;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      align-self: center;
    }
  }
</style>
